Poppy Montgomery https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poppy_Montgomery 0 Poppy Montgomery (born Poppy Petal Emma Elizabeth Deveraux Donaghue; 15 June 1972) is an Australian-American actress. She played FBI agent Samantha Spade on the CBS mystery drama Without a Trace from 2002 to 2009, and played Detective Carrie Wells on the CBS/A police drama Unforgettable from 2011 to 2016.
